# Requêtes pour tester les routes de AnswerController
# Variables :
# - Remplace {{baseUrl}} par l'URL où ton API tourne (ex: http://localhost:5000 ou https://localhost:5001)
# - Remplace {{jwt}} par un token JWT valide (les routes POST/PUT/DELETE nécessitent le rôle admin)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Get all answers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Answer
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Accept: application/json

### Get answer by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Answer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Accept: application/json

### Create an answer (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Answer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "title": "Réponse exemple",
  "questionId": 1,
  "isValid": true
}

### Update an answer (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Answer/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Réponse modifiée",
  "questionId": 1,
  "isValid": false
}

### Delete an answer (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Answer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
